<text id="02-output-contract" title="Fork vs Fix — Output Contract" version="1.0.0" est_tokens="700" depth="essential">
  <summary>Pins the shape of a `FixDecision` record per bug-blocking-upstream-library event.</summary>

  <section title="Required fields">
    <list>
      <item>`decision_id` — UUID</item>
      <item>`library` — object {name, ecosystem, current_version, bug_summary, repro_link}</item>
      <item>`axes` — array of 5 `{name ∈ {urgency, blast, patch_size, upstream_responsiveness, strategic_dependency}, score 0-3, evidence}`</item>
      <item>`total_score` — integer 0-15</item>
      <item>`action` — enum {workaround, monkey_patch, upstream_pr, fork_pin, replace}</item>
      <item>`action_playbook_url` — string</item>
      <item>`strategic_override_applied` — boolean</item>
      <item>`ban_list_blocked` — boolean (when monkey_patch was blocked by r5)</item>
      <item>`sunset_criterion` — string (required for fork_pin)</item>
      <item>`rollback_plan` — string</item>
      <item>`decided_by` — engineer identifier</item>
      <item>`decided_at` — ISO-8601</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <section title="Forbidden patterns">
    <antipattern>
      <description>`action: fork_pin` AND `sunset_criterion` empty.</description>
      <reason>Violates r4 fork hygiene.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>`action: monkey_patch` AND library in security-critical / framework-core ban list.</description>
      <reason>Violates r5.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>`axes.strategic_dependency.score == 3` AND `action ∈ {workaround, monkey_patch}`.</description>
      <reason>Violates r3 strategic override.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>`total_score != sum(axes[*].score)`.</description>
      <reason>Arithmetic inconsistency.</reason>
    </antipattern>
    <antipattern>
      <description>`action` does not match band per r2.</description>
      <reason>Decision must follow the rule; deviations require an explicit override field with justification.</reason>
    </antipattern>
  </section>

  <section title="Allowed transformations">
    <list>
      <item>Render decision as Markdown ADR alongside JSON for the repo's `decisions/` folder.</item>
      <item>Encrypt evidence URLs if they reference private repros.</item>
      <item>Aggregate by library across quarter for fork-audit dashboards.</item>
    </list>
  </section>

  <reference path="templates/fix-decision.json">FixDecision JSON Schema.</reference>
  <reference path="templates/fork-pin-playbook.md">Fork-pin step-by-step.</reference>
  <reference path="templates/upstream-pr-template.md">Upstream PR description.</reference>

  <section title="Self-check checklist">
    <list>
      <item>5 axes scored with evidence.</item>
      <item>Action matches band OR override justified.</item>
      <item>Strategic override + ban list applied.</item>
      <item>Fork sunset criterion present for fork_pin.</item>
      <item>Rollback plan defined.</item>
    </list>
  </section>
</text>
